c: 11
v: 78
t: "Uye vanhu vake vakauya vachimhanyidzana kwaari, sezvo mumashure vaigaro ita zvisakarurama (hungochani), iye akati: “Imi vanhu vangu! Ava vanasikana vangu (vakadzi vemunzvimbo), vakakuchenerai\t(kana\tmukavaroora\tzvakanaka).\tNokudaro\tityai\tAllah\tuye\tmusava munondinyadzisa maererano nevaenzi vangu! Hapana here murume akakwana pakati penyu?”"